</P>
<P>
 I give Bill Dwyre a gold for his commentary. Like the Wizard of Oz, the USOC 
is but a shell of the ideals they profess to exemplify. 
</P>
<P>
 If the USOC really wanted to reduce the controversy in Lillehammer, then they 
should have excluded the cause, one admitted liar, from the American team. 
Maybe the USOC should go to Oz and ask the Wizard for some heart, brains and 
courage. 
</P>
<P>
 GREGORY KILLIAN 
