<HEADLINE>
<P>
OSBOURNE SIGNING RESET FOR MARCH 15 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The comic book signing session by Ozzy Osbourne originally planned for Tuesday 
at the Golden Apple store in West Hollywood has been rescheduled for March 15 
due to changes in Osbourne's recording schedule.  
</P>
<P>
 Osbourne will be signing copies of a new comic book based on his life story. 
The appearance is scheduled to take place from 4 to 7 p.m. at Golden Apple, 
7711 Melrose Ave. 
</P>
