<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA021994-0227 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 015057 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 19, 1994, Saturday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 6; Metro Desk 
