in the Atlanta Journal-Constitution after Dan Jansen's failure last Monday in 
the 500-meter speedskating. 
</P>
<P>
 "Here's the good news: Jansen gets another chance Friday in the 1,000 meters. 
Here's the bad news: Jansen will blow it again." 
</P>
<P>
 Uh, no, Terence, here's the good news. . . . MIKE DOWNEY 
