<HEADLINE>
<P>
OBITUARIES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Aupiu, Tanu Savea Jr., 52, of Oxnard, machine operator at Northrop Corp. James 
A. Reardon Mortuary, Oxnard. 
</P>
<P>
 Bankston, Ethel, 68, of Oxnard, retired residential care provider. James A. 
Reardon Mortuary, Oxnard. 
</P>
<P>
 Furkona, Nick, 78, of Ventura. Ted Mayr Funeral Home, Ventura. 
</P>
<P>
 Spies, Ed, 78, of Ventura, engineer at Northrop Corp. Ted Mayr Funeral Home, 
Ventura. 
</P>
<P>
 Starn, Sophia, 78, of Reseda, formerly of Simi Valley, homemaker. Pierce 
Brothers Valhalla Mortuary, North Hollywood. 
</P>
<P>
 Weber, Margaret E., 76, of Newbury Park, retired nurse at Veterans 
Administration Hospital in West Los Angeles. Pierce Brothers Griffin Mortuary, 
Thousand Oaks. 
</P>
<P>
 Ventura County obituaries are published free of charge as a public service to 
readers. Obituaries are based on information provided by mortuaries. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
